## Suggest without keyword - `↵` to search - `⌘↵` to open first link ("Feeling Lucky") - `⌘↵` to copy first link (requires [searchlink](https://github.com/ttscoff/searchlink))
It is recommended to deactivate Google as Fallback Search.
## Global Search Hotkey If selection is… - file path: reveal it in Finder - directory path: open directory in Finder - url: open in default browser - email: send eMail to that address - some other text: search for it & open first duckduckgo hit ("I'm feeling lucky") - empty: do nothing
---
